# 🛡️ Welcome to the GuardAurora Wiki

GuardAurora is an AI-powered safety application designed to protect girls and children in real-life situations by detecting threats and responding automatically.

This wiki provides additional information about the project, including its architecture, features, and development roadmap.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

GuardAurora focuses on **preventive safety**, using artificial intelligence to detect potential danger without requiring manual interaction from the user.

The system analyzes environmental audio, detects abnormal or threatening patterns, and activates emergency protocols such as recording, alerting trusted contacts, and sharing real-time location.

---

## 🚀 Core Features

* AI-based sound and voice analysis
* Automatic emergency response
* Real-time GPS tracking
* Chatbot and voice assistant
* Safe route suggestions (“Where are you?” feature)

